<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NURUL HIDAYAH | CYBER LAB v5.0</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <!-- Library Partikel (Wajib Online) -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net"></script>
    <style>
        /* Base Cyber Theme */
        body { background: #000c1d; color: #add8e6; overflow-x: hidden; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; cursor: crosshair; }
        #particles-js { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; z-index: 1; pointer-events: none; }
        
        /* Bingkai Custom: Atas Bulat, Bawah Tajam */
        .cyber-box {
            background: rgba(1, 28, 50, 0.85);
            border: 2px solid #00f2ff; /* Biru Muda */
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 242, 255, 0.3);
            border-radius: 30px 30px 0 0; /* Atas Bulat */
            clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 100% 90%, 90% 100%, 0 100%); /* Bawah Tajam */
            position: relative;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            z-index: 10;
        }
        .cyber-box:hover { 
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px #00f2ff; 
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            background: rgba(1, 40, 70, 0.9);
        }

        /* Animasi Binary HIJAU */
        .bin-char {
            position: fixed; color: #00ff00; font-weight: bold; pointer-events: none;
            text-shadow: 0 0 8px #00ff00; z-index: 1000; animation: explode 0.8s ease-out forwards;
        }
        @keyframes explode {
            0% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1.5); opacity: 1; }
            100% { transform: translate(var(--tx), var(--ty)) rotate(360deg) scale(0); opacity: 0; }
        }

        .neon-blue { text-shadow: 0 0 15px #00f2ff; color: #00f2ff; }
    </style>
</head>
<body onmousedown="spawnBinary(event)">
    <!-- Particle Background (Neural Link Putih) -->
    <div id="particles-js"></div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-10 relative z-50">
        
        <!-- HEADER -->
        <header class="flex justify-between items-start mb-12">
            <div class="w-16 h-24 cyber-box flex items-center justify-center opacity-70">
                <span class="text-[8px] text-center font-bold">PALESTINE<br>MAP</span>
            </div>
            <div class="text-right">
                <h1 class="text-5xl font-black neon-blue tracking-widest uppercase italic">NURUL HIDAYAH SCHOOL</h1>
                <div class="h-1 w-full bg-gradient-to-l from-cyan-400 to-transparent mt-2"></div>
            </div>
        </header>

        <!-- FOTO DOKUMENTASI BESAR -->
        <div class="cyber-box p-2 mb-20 mx-auto max-w-5xl">
            <div class="bg-cyan-950 h-80 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden relative rounded-t-[28px]">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://source.unsplash.com')] bg-cover opacity-40"></div>
                <span class="relative z-10 text-lg tracking-[0.5em] font-black uppercase neon-blue animate-pulse">DOKUMENTASI MURID</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 8 BINGKAI GURU -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-24">
            <script>
                const teachers = [
                    {n: "IMAT JUNAEDAH.SPDI", r: "KEPALA SEKOLAH"},
                    {n: "ATANG ABDURAHMAN", r: "MANAGER"},
                    {n: "MASPUPAH.SPD", r: "GURU/SEKERTARIS"},
                    {n: "APIPULLOH ASHIDIQ.S.TI", r: "OPERATOR"},
                    {n: "SRI INDAH", r: "GURU"},
                    {n: "NABILA FAUZAIAH", r: "GURU"},
                    {n: "SALWA NOVIYANTI", r: "GURU"},
                    {n: "GURU_ACTIVE", r: "GURU"}
                ];
                teachers.forEach(t => {
                    document.write(`
                        <div class="group">
                            <div class="cyber-box p-2 mb-3">
                                <div class="bg-cyan-900/40 h-36 flex items-center justify-center rounded-t-[25px] overflow-hidden">
                                     <img src="https://api.dicebear.com{t.n}" class="w-20 h-20 opacity-80 group-hover:scale-110 transition">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="bg-cyan-400 text-black text-[9px] font-black py-2 tracking-widest text-center uppercase shadow-[0_0_10px_#00f2ff]">
                                ${t.n}<br><span class="text-[7px] opacity-70 font-normal">${t.r}</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    `);
                });
            </script>
        </div>

        <!-- VISI & MISI (2 KOLOM) -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 mb-24">
            <div class="cyber-box p-8 border-l-4 border-cyan-400">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-black mb-6 italic underline neon-blue">1. KB NURUL HIDAYAH (PAUD)</h3>
                <div class="text-[11px] space-y-3 opacity-90 leading-relaxed">
                    <p class="font-bold text-cyan-300 italic">"Membentuk generasi Rabbani yang unggul, berakhlak mulia, dan adaptif terhadap teknologi sejak usia dini."</p>
                    <p>• PAI: Internalisasi nilai Islami & Akhlakul Karimah (Fun Learning).</p>
                    <p>• TEKNOLOGI: Multimedia Interaktif & Literasi Digital Aman.</p>
                    <p>• METODE: Kurikulum berbasis TIK untuk visualisasi spiritual.</p>
                    <p>• TUJUAN: Anak cerdas, kreatif, mandiri, dan berkarakter siap pendidikan dasar.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cyber-box p-8 border-r-4 border-cyan-400">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-black mb-6 italic underline neon-blue">2. MADRASAH DINIYAH (MD)</h3>
                <div class="text-[11px] space-y-3 opacity-90 leading-relaxed">
                    <p class="font-bold text-cyan-300 italic">"Pendidikan Islam Rahmatan lil 'Alamiin dengan penguasaan Ulumuddin mendalam."</p>
                    <p>• AKADEMIK: Tarbiyah, Ta'lim, & Ta'dib untuk pembentukan Adab.</p>
                    <p>• KOMPETENSI: Pedagogik, Profesional Keilmuan, & Uswah Hasanah.</p>
                    <p>• LINGKUNGAN: Islamic Environment terintegrasi teknologi digital.</p>
                    <p>• INTEGRITAS: Karakter mulia berbasis tanggung jawab moral.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- SEJARAH PENDIRIAN (KH. MUSTOFA) -->
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-24">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-black tracking-[0.4em] uppercase mb-1 neon-blue">SEJARAH PENDIRIAN</h2>
            <div class="cyber-box w-56 h-56 mx-auto mb-6 p-4 flex items-center justify-center">
                <div class="border-2 border-dashed border-cyan-500 w-full h-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center opacity-60 rounded-t-[20px]">
                    <span class="text-[10px] font-bold">KH. MUSTOFA.MUI</span>
                    <span class="text-[8px] uppercase tracking-widest mt-2">[ PENDIRI ]</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cyber-box p-8 text-[12px] leading-relaxed text-justify italic bg-cyan-900/10 border-t-4 border-cyan-400">
                "Ponpes Nurul Hidayah didirikan dengan tekad mulia KH. MUSTOFA untuk menyinergikan kecerdasan intelektual dan kedalaman spiritual. Berawal dari langkah kecil penuh perjuangan, sekolah ini bertumbuh menjadi institusi yang menjaga amanah pembentukan karakter generasi masa depan yang cerdas secara spiritual dan mahir secara teknologi."
            </div>
        </div>

        <footer class="flex justify-center opacity-30 pb-10">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 border border-cyan-500 rotate-45"></div>
        </footer>
    </div>

    <script>
        // BACKGROUND PARTIKEL PUTIH (Neural Connection)
        particlesJS("particles-js", {
            "particles": {
                "number": { "value": 120, "density": { "enable": true, "value_area": 800 } },
                "color": { "value": "#ffffff" }, // WARNA PUTIH
                "shape": { "type": "circle" },
                "opacity": { "value": 0.6 },
                "size": { "value": 3 },
                "line_linked": { "enable": true, "distance": 150, "color": "#ffffff", "opacity": 0.4, "width": 1 },
                "move": { "enable": true, "speed": 3, "direction": "none", "out_mode": "out" }
            },
            "interactivity": { "events": { "onhover": { "enable": true, "mode": "grab" } } }
        });

        // ANIMASI BINARY HIJAU (Saat Klik)
        function spawnBinary(e) {
            for(let i=0; i<15; i++) {
                const b = document.createElement('div');
                b.className = 'bin-char';
                b.innerText = Math.random() > 0.5 ? "1" : "0";
                const tx = (Math.random() - 0.5) * 350 + "px";
                const ty = (Math.random() - 0.5) * 350 + "px";
                b.style.setProperty('--tx', tx);
                b.style.setProperty('--ty', ty);
                b.style.left = e.clientX + "px";
                b.style.top = e.clientY + "px";
                document.body.appendChild(b);
                setTimeout(() => b.remove(), 800);
            }
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
